---
/* Differentiators section - light themed with 3 differentiator cards */
---

<section id="diferenciadores" class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section heading -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="uppercase text-sm tracking-widest font-semibold text-amber-500 mb-3">
        POR QUÉ ELEGIRNOS
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center">
        Lo que nos hace diferentes
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Differentiator cards grid -->
    <div class="stagger-children grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <!-- 1. Inversión inteligente -->
      <div class="fade-in-up bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-amber-50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-amber-500" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 2l4 7h-8l4-7z" />
            <path d="M16 9l4 7H4l4-7" />
            <path d="M8 16l-4 6h16l-4-6" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Inversión inteligente</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Alto impacto sin la sobrecarga de las grandes consultoras. Soluciones a medida que maximizan cada peso invertido.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. Resultados que se ven -->
      <div class="fade-in-up bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-amber-50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-amber-500" aria-hidden="true">
            <polyline points="22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17" />
            <polyline points="16 7 22 7 22 13" />
            <path d="M8 20l2 2 4-4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Resultados que se ven</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Métricas claras desde el día uno. Checkpoints de ajuste para asegurar que cada acción genera valor medible.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Socios, no proveedores -->
      <div class="fade-in-up bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-amber-50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-amber-500" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="9" cy="8" r="3" />
            <circle cx="15" cy="8" r="3" />
            <path d="M3 21v-2a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h2" />
            <path d="M21 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4h-2" />
            <path d="M12 17v4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Socios, no proveedores</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Relaciones de largo plazo construidas sobre confianza y resultados. Tu éxito es nuestro éxito.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
